  "page": "A Game of Thrones (comics)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2; text-align:center; font-style: italic;\">George R.R. Martin's A Game of Thrones</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Author</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniel_Abraham_(author)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Daniel Abraham (author)\">Daniel Abraham</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Country</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:United States\">United States</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Language</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/English_language\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:English language\">English</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Series</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Genre(s)</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fantasy\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Fantasy\">Fantasy</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Publisher</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamite_Entertainment\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Dynamite Entertainment\">Dynamite Entertainment</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Released</th><td>\n21 September 2011 – 30 July 2014</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Illustrator</th><td>\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/tommy-patterson/4040-56598/\">Tommy Patterson</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Cover Artist</th><td>\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mike_S._Miller\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Mike S. Miller\">Mike S. Miller</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Media Type</th><td>\nComics</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Followed&#160;by</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings_(comics)\" title=\"A Clash of Kings (comics)\">George R.R. Martin's A Clash of Kings</a></i></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>George R.R. Martin's A Game of Thrones</b></i> is a <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/comic_book\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:comic book\">comic book</a> adaptation of <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a>'s fantasy novel <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, the first in the <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> series. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Production\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Production</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Publication_history\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publication history</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Collections\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Collections</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Production\">Production</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Game_of_Thrones_(comics)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Production\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The comic book series is scripted by fantasy author <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniel_Abraham_(author)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Daniel Abraham (author)\">Daniel Abraham</a> and drawn by Tommy Patterson, with covers by Patterson and by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mike_S._Miller\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Mike S. Miller\">Mike S. Miller</a>. It was intended to follow the story and atmosphere of the novel closely, at a rate of about a page of art for each page of text, and covered 24 issues of 29 pages each. Martin advised Abraham on aspects of the adaptation.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Comic_Book_Resources_21_September_2011_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Comic_Book_Resources_21_September_2011-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publication_history\">Publication history</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Game_of_Thrones_(comics)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Publication history\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The initial issue was published by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dynamite_Entertainment\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Dynamite Entertainment\">Dynamite Entertainment</a> in September 2011.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Geeks_of_Doom_21_September_2011_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Geeks_of_Doom_21_September_2011-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> New issues were published at a rate of one per month. The series concluded with the 24th issue on July 30, 2014.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Covers of the first 9 issues:\n</p>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Comics1_Cover.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Comics1 Cover.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c4/Comics1_Cover.jpg/80px-Comics1_Cover.jpg\" width=\"80\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c4/Comics1_Cover.jpg/120px-Comics1_Cover.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c4/Comics1_Cover.jpg/160px-Comics1_Cover.jpg 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Comics2_Cover.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Comics2 Cover.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/4c/Comics2_Cover.jpg/80px-Comics2_Cover.jpg\" width=\"80\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/4c/Comics2_Cover.jpg/120px-Comics2_Cover.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/4c/Comics2_Cover.jpg/160px-Comics2_Cover.jpg 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Comics3_Cover.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Comics3 Cover.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/30/Comics3_Cover.jpg/80px-Comics3_Cover.jpg\" width=\"80\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/30/Comics3_Cover.jpg/120px-Comics3_Cover.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/30/Comics3_Cover.jpg/160px-Comics3_Cover.jpg 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Comics4_Cover.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Comics4 Cover.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/Comics4_Cover.jpg/80px-Comics4_Cover.jpg\" width=\"80\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/Comics4_Cover.jpg/120px-Comics4_Cover.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fe/Comics4_Cover.jpg/160px-Comics4_Cover.jpg 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Comics5_Cover.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Comics5 Cover.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/59/Comics5_Cover.jpg/80px-Comics5_Cover.jpg\" width=\"80\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/59/Comics5_Cover.jpg/120px-Comics5_Cover.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/59/Comics5_Cover.jpg/160px-Comics5_Cover.jpg 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Comics6_Cover.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Comics6 Cover.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/Comics6_Cover.jpg/80px-Comics6_Cover.jpg\" width=\"80\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/Comics6_Cover.jpg/120px-Comics6_Cover.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/Comics6_Cover.jpg/160px-Comics6_Cover.jpg 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Comic_cover_07.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Comic cover 07.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f8/Comic_cover_07.jpg/80px-Comic_cover_07.jpg\" width=\"80\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f8/Comic_cover_07.jpg/120px-Comic_cover_07.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f8/Comic_cover_07.jpg/160px-Comic_cover_07.jpg 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Comics8_Cover.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Comics8 Cover.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/36/Comics8_Cover.jpg/80px-Comics8_Cover.jpg\" width=\"80\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/36/Comics8_Cover.jpg/120px-Comics8_Cover.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/36/Comics8_Cover.jpg/160px-Comics8_Cover.jpg 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Comics9_Cover.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Comics9 Cover.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/55/Comics9_Cover.jpg/80px-Comics9_Cover.jpg\" width=\"80\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/55/Comics9_Cover.jpg/120px-Comics9_Cover.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/55/Comics9_Cover.jpg/160px-Comics9_Cover.jpg 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Collections\">Collections</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Game_of_Thrones_(comics)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Collections\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Four sets of six issues each were published by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bantam_Books\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Bantam Books\">Bantam Books</a> as <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trade_paperback_(comics)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Trade paperback (comics)\">trade paperbacks</a>, marketed as a <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/graphic_novel\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:graphic novel\">graphic novel</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Comics_Beat_13_December_2011_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Comics_Beat_13_December_2011-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> The first volume, published on March 27, 2012, took first place on the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_New_York_Times_Best_Seller_list\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:The New York Times Best Seller list\"><i>New York Times</i> best-seller list</a> for graphic books the day after its publication.<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> The second volume was released on June 11, 2013 and featured issues 7 though 12. Issues 13 through 18 were released in a third volume on March 11, 2014. A fourth volume containing the last six issues was published May 5, 2015.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Title</th>\n<th>ISBN</th>\n<th>Date of publication</th>\n<th>Contains\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><i>A Game of Thrones: The Graphic Novel: Volume One</i>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php/Special:BookSources/978-0-440-42321-8\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-440-42321-8\">978-0-440-42321-8</a>\n</td>\n<td>March 27, 2012\n</td>\n<td><i>A Game of Thrones</i> #1–6<br />The Making of <i>A Game of Thrones: The Graphic Novel: Volume One</i>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><i>A Game of Thrones: The Graphic Novel: Volume Two</i>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php/Special:BookSources/978-0-007-49304-3\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-007-49304-3\">978-0-007-49304-3</a>\n</td>\n<td>June 11, 2013\n</td>\n<td><i>A Game of Thrones</i> #7–12\n<p>The Making of <i>A Game of Thrones: The Graphic Novel: Volume Two</i>\n</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><i>A Game of Thrones: The Graphic Novel: Volume Three</i>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php/Special:BookSources/978-0-440-42323-2\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-440-42323-2\">978-0-440-42323-2</a>\n</td>\n<td>March 11, 2014\n</td>\n<td><i>A Game of Thrones</i> #13-18\n<p>The Making of <i>A Game of Thrones: The Graphic Novel: Volume Three</i>\n</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><i>A Game of Thrones: The Graphic Novel: Volume Four</i>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php/Special:BookSources/978-0-345-52919-0\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-345-52919-0\">978-0-345-52919-0</a>\n</td>\n<td>May 5, 2015\n</td>\n<td><i>A Game of Thrones</i> #19-24\n<p>The Making of <i>A Game of Thrones: The Graphic Novel: Volume Four</i>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Game_of_Thrones_(comics)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Comic_Book_Resources_21_September_2011-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Comic_Book_Resources_21_September_2011_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><span class=\"citation web\">Sunu,&#32;Steve&#32;(21 September 2011).&#32;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&amp;id=34496\">\"Abraham Plays \"A Game of Thrones\"\"</a><span class=\"printonly\">.&#32;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&amp;id=34496\">http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&amp;id=34496</a></span><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">.&#32;Retrieved 1 October 2011</span>.</span><span class=\"Z3988\" title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Abraham+Plays+%22A+Game+of+Thrones%22&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Sunu&amp;rft.aufirst=Steve&amp;rft.au=Sunu%2C%26%2332%3BSteve&amp;rft.date=21+September+2011&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.comicbookresources.com%2F%3Fpage%3Darticle%26id%3